  entries:
  - mechanic: 0
    title: How to play
    description: I will use my pen to draw the artwork customers have in mind.
  - mechanic: 1
    title: Time limit
    description: The stopwatch shows how much time I have left for a drawing.
  - mechanic: 2
    title: Selling
    description: If I am done early, I can sell immediately by hitting the bell.
  - mechanic: 3
    title: Colors
    description: I can select my new colors by using the palette on the left.
  - mechanic: 4
    title: Daily shift
    description: The line at the bottom shows how far I am in my daily shift.
  - mechanic: 5
    title: Customers
    description: It seems every customer is different. Some of them don't like my
      art as much as others.
  - mechanic: 6
    title: Rush hour
    description: The tinted section of the daily shift line is a rush hour period.
      My time limit will be stricter!
  - mechanic: 7
    title: Bad weather
    description: On days with extreme weather, not as many guests come around, so
      I work a shorter shift.
  - mechanic: 8
    title: Events
    description: Today seems to be a special event. The kinds of drawings people
      request me to draw might change.
  - mechanic: 9
    title: Followers
    description: I'm gaining quite a few followers. If this keeps up, I might become
      popular online!
  - mechanic: 10
    title: Rainy days
    description: Not as many people come around on rainy days, but they bring out
      some unusual folk as well.
